name: Happy 28th Birthday!
tagline: Kanye West challenges you to a game of Crypto Catch.
body:
### You're 28!
And we know what that means: you're only getting further away from your peak gaming skillz. I know how much you've wanted to play games together, so, for your birthday, I build you one. I hope you can beat it.

### Kanye's Crypto Catch
Kanye was not harmed during the production of this game. 
<iframe allowtransparency="true" width="485" height="402" src="http://scratch.mit.edu/projects/embed/108723806/?autostart=false" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

### Support and Credit
Having trouble with the game? Contact your GF and she'll help you sort it out. Inspired by GWalker's Pikachu Game via the CS50 Website.
